                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Key Insights</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• 93% of students were successfully placed.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Students with CGPA above 8 achieved the highest placement success.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Students with 2 or more internships achieved nearly 100% placement rates.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Completing 2 or more projects significantly improved placement chances.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Students with more certifications were mostly classified as High Chance candidates.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Most students are expected to receive packages between 5–12 LPA, with the highest package reaching 12 LPA.</run>
                </formatted-text>
